[Progress in the surgical treatment of the patellar fracture].

[Article in Chinese; Abstract available in Chinese from the publisher]

Li G(1), Liu P(1)(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopedics, Liyuan Hospital Affiliated to Tongji Medical 
School of Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Wuhan Hubei, 430077, 
P.R.China.
(2)Physical Examination Center, Liyuan Hospital Affiliated to Tongji Medical 
School of Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Wuhan Hubei, 430077, 
