2-year outcomes of ranibizumab versus laser therapy for the treatment of very 
low birthweight infants with retinopathy of prematurity (RAINBOW extension 
study): prospective follow-up of an open label, randomised controlled trial.

Marlow N(1), Stahl A(2), Lepore D(3), Fielder A(4), Reynolds JD(5), Zhu Q(6), 
Weisberger A(7), Stiehl DP(8), Fleck B(9); RAINBOW investigators group.

